actions.message:
`b!name` - Enter your ingame name or id in this field
`b!guild` - Enter the name of your current guild/clan here
`b!characters` - Enter the amount of characters you have obtained
`b!scores` - Enter your Max guild score here
`b!pvpseat` - Enter your current brave battle seat here
`b!aboutme` - An extra space to give a little bit more info about yourself

`b!profile` - Use this command to view your profile!

actions.message:
__***THE FINAL BOUT***__

This round is a **straight up speedrun.** Enough fooling around with limited characters and accessories, it’s time to let loose. 

*Any character*, slotted or non slotted, golden or non golden accessories **will be allowed**. Since we’ve had a *talk about both finalist’s accounts* beforehand to confirm **nobody has a real advantage** over the other, there’s no room to complain about unfairness afterwards. 

May the best player win and be crowned the ***Speed King of Zero Division!***
